==English==
===Etymology===
Portmanteau of '''[[scan]]''' and '''[[translate]]'''.

===Noun===
'''scanlation''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

# The process of scanning and translating Korean or Japanese manga for free distribution over the Internet, especially into Western languages such as [[English]], [[French]], and [[Spanish]].

